Datasource.Parameter: (SELECT gid, geom FROM geom_polygon_world_boundary) AS world_land
(SELECT gid, kind, geom FROM geom_polygon_china_water_primary) AS china_water_primary
(SELECT gid, kind, geom FROM geom_line_china_southsea_9) AS china_southsea_9
(SELECT gid, kind, geom FROM geom_line_china_province_primary) AS china_province_primary
(SELECT gid, kind, geom FROM geom_line_china_mainland_primary WHERE kind <> '013e') AS china_boundary_primary

(SELECT gid, link_kind, func_cls, geom FROM geom_line_china_route_link WHERE (func_cls = 2 OR link_kind = 2) AND NOT link_type && '{"03", "05", "06", "07", "0a", "12", "13", "14", "15", "16", "17"}') AS data

(SELECT gid, link_kind, func_cls, geom FROM geom_line_china_route_link WHERE (func_cls = 1 OR link_kind = 0 OR link_kind = 1) AND NOT link_type && '{"03", "05", "06", "07", "0a", "12", "13", "14", "15", "16", "17"}') AS data

(SELECT gid, link_kind, func_cls, width, CASE WHEN link_type && '{"03", "04", "05", "07", "0b", "0e"}' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END is_trib, geom FROM geom_line_china_route_link WHERE draw_lvl = 5 ORDER BY speed_cls DESC) AS data

(SELECT gid, link_kind, func_cls, width, CASE WHEN link_type && '{"03", "04", "05", "07", "0b", "0e"}' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END is_trib, geom FROM geom_line_china_route_link WHERE draw_lvl = 4 ORDER BY speed_cls DESC) AS data

(SELECT gid, link_kind, func_cls, width, CASE WHEN link_type && '{"03", "04", "05", "07", "0b", "0e"}' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END is_trib, geom FROM geom_line_china_route_link WHERE draw_lvl = 3 ORDER BY speed_cls DESC) AS data

(SELECT gid, link_kind, func_cls, width, CASE WHEN link_type && '{"03", "04", "05", "07", "0b", "0e"}' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END is_trib, geom FROM geom_line_china_route_link WHERE draw_lvl = 2 ORDER BY is_trib DESC) AS data

(SELECT gid, link_kind, func_cls, width, CASE WHEN link_type && '{"03", "04", "05", "07", "0b", "0e"}' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END is_trib, CASE WHEN link_type && '{"04", "05"}' AND NOT link_type && '{"06", "07"}' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END is_ic, geom FROM geom_line_china_route_link WHERE draw_lvl = 1 ORDER BY is_trib DESC) AS data
(SELECT gid, kind, feat_name, feat_name_abbr, LENGTH(feat_name) ref_len, LENGTH(feat_name_abbr) ref_abbr_len, geom FROM label_point_china_regions) AS data
(SELECT gid, name, name kind, geom FROM geom_point_world_cities) AS label_world_cities
(SELECT gid, route_kind, draw_lvl, feat_name, LENGTH(feat_name) ref_len, geom FROM shield_line_china_route ORDER BY draw_lvl, route_kind) AS data
(SELECT gid, draw_lvl, func_cls, feat_name, geom FROM label_line_china_route WHERE name_type = 0 ORDER BY draw_lvl, St_Length(geom)) AS data
